{"tid":473760,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［你會點簡］你身家有一百萬其實又有咩用？","createTime":"2017-11-19T13:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T04:16:14.000Z","uid":47920,"like":8,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"54244497dd032f516799991a8be720b0302a8f3b","tid":473760,"uid":47920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"當你19幾歲有一百萬。你會選擇係香港到做樓奴定係會出外國讀書？如果係後者用完依一百萬就會身冇分文，要即刻搵野做。<br />\n<br />\n我係後者。但當我讀完書，我又係到諗其實一百萬為左張沙紙值唔值得呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實可能你睇完我依個選擇覺得我好傻仔。比一百萬去讀書，但我又覺得係香港既一百萬根本唔係錢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地又會點選擇<br />\n樓奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外國讀屎片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f57acad50c5b6c0fd37d915e9bfde6a0076278","tid":473760,"uid":47920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f9bdba8da97551c03e1bdb43eb7f189323099f","tid":473760,"uid":86500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:50:43.000Z","msg":"樓主19歲有100萬？"},{"pid":"7a08d8254c2e295a6cf5f3be56b5d8c98a877e0a","tid":473760,"uid":74858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:51:45.000Z","msg":"我係讀書"},{"pid":"c43d60d368447c2bc1a679ef4492f87e4cf3509c","tid":473760,"uid":47920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主19歲有100萬？</blockquote><br />\n你就當有一百萬比我用"},{"pid":"81acb5ca6d5d39eaa3e96558006745baa7558508","tid":473760,"uid":47920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係讀書</blockquote><br />\n利申：係香港讀唔成書。變左係外國讀。其實成日諗係ive讀係唔係差唔多"},{"pid":"cd6c55ebfaf312b6f6a3a5305622c5510cd06d97","tid":473760,"uid":107184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:55:53.000Z","msg":"環遊世界 u only live once 梗係玩盡佢"},{"pid":"ca8dabbb104dc3286cd68d16a6dddb33ff3ccde4","tid":473760,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"去外國讀留得低既科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0173d09f94d80d5122b1a9aaeef0096b94121f","tid":473760,"uid":47920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去外國讀留得低既科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩意思？"},{"pid":"f8118495ce729da7c8f85e4b55694e0dbdb90df1","tid":473760,"uid":47920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>環遊世界 u only live once 梗係玩盡佢</blockquote><br />\n如果有咁既錢我都想。但宜家得兩個選擇。一個係即刻做樓奴，另一個係遲四五年做拎著沙紙既樓奴"},{"pid":"b97bee6b31518accd440b22409c86b36b46c4f99","tid":473760,"uid":47920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8582f354844f63503538cfdf6166b1798691c57b","tid":473760,"uid":56308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"呢個問題我都好糾結，屋企人成日話等我畢業之後幫我比首期。但意味著我之後就要揹負住層樓幾十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7b5384a56b82ee4aad4b0e3397d986187bea9c","tid":473760,"uid":47920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個問題我都好糾結，屋企人成日話等我畢業之後幫我比首期。但意味著我之後就要揹負住層樓幾十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但我係只有一百萬讀完書就冇。之後連供樓都要全部自己供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323f94bc1c4f136a767ccf491e44e753b2f73e4e","tid":473760,"uid":45431,"like":